iToday is March 27th, 19 days since the disappearance of MH370.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iWith no progress in locating the aircraft, various theories about its		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ifate have emerged. Both the mid-air disintegration and pilot hijacking		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ihypotheses have flaws (the former has been ruled out). Recently,		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iCanadian pilot Chris Goodfellow analyzed that the plane might have		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
icaught fire, causing communication system failure.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
